    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Refers to the cultures of the continent of North America, which is bounded by the Atlantic Ocean, the Pacific Ocean, the Arctic Circle, and Central America. In classifications schemes based on physical geography, Central America, and North America are parts of the same continent.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
